Package: hashwatcher-hub-pi
Version: __VERSION__
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.9), python3-venv, python3-pip, python3-dev, python3-dbus, bluetooth, bluez, libbluetooth-dev, libglib2.0-dev, libdbus-1-dev, libcairo2-dev, libgirepository1.0-dev, gobject-introspection, pkg-config, meson, network-manager, curl
Recommends: tailscale
Maintainer: Engineered Essentials <support@hashwatcher.app>
Homepage: https://www.hashwatcher.app
Description: HashWatcher Hub Pi — Raspberry Pi mining hub agent
 Monitors BitAxe/BitDSK/NerdQ miners on the local network, provides a
 web dashboard on port 8787, BLE Wi-Fi provisioning, and Tailscale
 subnet routing for remote access via the HashWatcher iOS app.
